OL,7,FBritain's most famous street cleaner
OL,8,Fsaid he was thrilled to be on the trip
OL,9,Fof a lifetime in Portugal after
OL,10,Fgetting a brilliant birthday surprise.
OL,12,FA holiday company gifted Paul Spiers
OL,13,Fthe trip abroad after an online
OL,14,Ffundraiser by residents in Beckenham
OL,15,Fbroke rules of his employment.
OL,17,FITV News London caught up with Paul as
OL,18,Fhe soaked up the sun and he described
OL,19,Ffeeling "gobsmacked" by the generosity
OL,20,Fof those who made the trip possible.
