OL,7,F"No words can describe how grateful I
OL,8,Fam... We took a walk along the beach
OL,9,Fand we went to the cafe and the market
OL,10,Fstalls," Paul said.
OL,12,F"Maybe I'll go on a boat trip and
OL,13,Fmaybe see some dolphins," he added.
OL,15,FPaul noticed how clean the streets
OL,16,Fwere in Portugal and wished he could
OL,17,Fkeep them looking that good in South
OL,18,FLondon.
