OL,4,Cthrilled to be on the trip of a
OL,5,Clifetime
OL,7,FPaul added: "It's absolutely superb
OL,8,Fand we've for another few days to go
OL,9,Fyet.
OL,11,F"I'm hoping to come back again in a
OL,12,Ffew years' time - it will take me a
OL,13,Fbit longer to save up the money."
OL,15,FPaul has been to Portugal once before
OL,16,Fand stayed in the same hotel. He said
OL,17,Fhe felt very fond of the area.
OL,19,FBut he might look at going somewhere
OL,20,Felse next time he leaves to UK on
OL,21,Fholiday - possibly Spain.
