OL,7,FThe online fundraising page which
OL,8,Fraised more than #3,000 was set up by
OL,9,Flocal resident Lisa Knight who was
OL,10,Fdelighted that Paul managed to get
OL,11,Faway.
OL,13,F"It's really lovely, I've been in
OL,14,Ftouch with him every day," Lisa told
OL,15,FITV News London.
OL,17,F"I'm really glad he is having a lovely
OL,18,Ftime. I'm so happy he got his dream
OL,19,Fholiday and is being looked after by
OL,20,Fhis brother David," she added.
